data.description: Two-story, 5 bedroom 3 bathroom home, nestled within a peaceful neighborhood near The Chimneys golf course, retail and a new hospital under construction. This spacious open-concept home showcases a delightful kitchen that seamlessly connects to the welcoming family room, offering a harmonious living space. This includes a bedroom and full bath on the main floor. On the second level you’ll find the large Primary Suite, complete with a walk-in closet, its own retreat currently setup as a private movie room, a conveniently located laundry room, another full bathroom, and three generously sized secondary bedrooms. The expansive, private backyard, enclosed by a sturdy fence, a separate fenced area for pets, boasts a charming patio, ideal for outdoor gatherings. There is a utility building for storage. This vibrant neighborhood has a community pool, Bath house with an area to cookout along with a playground, sidewalks, and enjoys a prime location, with easy access to schools, shopping centers.
